title: SUNNY, HUGE, PERFECTLY LOCATED 1 BEDROOM RIGHT OFF OF PARK ST,DOWNTOWN
posting_body: ['SUNNY, HUGE, PERFECTLY LOCATED 1 BEDROOM RIGHT OFF OF PARK ST (DOWNTOWN ALAMEDA)', '2410 Lincoln Avenue #A is a HUGE (approx.', '1000 sq ft) 1-bedroom 1-bathroom in downtown Alameda, right off of Park Street.', 'The sunlit-filled unit has brand new carpet floors throughout and tile floors in the updated kitchen and bathroom.', 'This apartment is only a short stroll away from all of the restaurants and shops Downtown Alameda has to offer.', 'The Alameda Movie Theater is only a few blocks away.', 'The updated kitchen features:', 'Gas stove', 'Dishwasher', 'Brand new Quartz countertops', 'Brand new tile backsplash', 'Brand new refrigerator', 'Brand new stainless steel sink and faucet', 'The rooms are spacious with endless storage; not only are there countless kitchen cabinets, but the apartment includes FIVE storage closets!', 'Two of the closets are attached to the bedroom.', 'There is also a brand new ceiling fan in the bedroom (with a remote!)', 'Tenant pays gas, electricity and water.', 'No rental fee.', 'Coin laundry on-site.', 'Street parking.', 'No pets.', 'Lease terms: 1 year lease', 'Rent: $2600', 'Security deposit: $2600', 'Must have good credit, and 3x rent income.', 'No rental fee', 'Pet: None', 'Tenant pays gas, electric, and water', 'Parking: Street', 'Coin-op laundry', 'Call Audra to schedule a viewing.', 'Viewings available 7 days a week.', 'FIVE 1 ZERO - THREE 8 FOUR - 7 NINE 4 ZERO', 'Thank you.']
